title: Minecraft_v1.8.1.zip
description:
Minecraft Launcher by Team Extreme.

Originally uploaded by user VIruz from here = https://kat.cr/user/VIruz/

I couldn't find a download anywhere of this so I thought I would upload it as it's one of the best.



Simply unzip and install, It will update to the latest version of the launcher and you can choose which version of minecraft you want to run in the drop down list.

All versions of minecraft will be listed including the very latest versions
